on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7774q8e_sharad-pawar_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntense%20negotiations%20are%20underway%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20was%20recently%20in%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20for%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20MVA%2FINDIA%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Bal%20Thackeray%2C%20or%20'UBT')%2C%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%2C%C2%A0%20aims%20to%20build%20on%20the%20momentum%20from%20the%20general%20elections%20and%20challenge%20the%20Mahayuti%2FNational%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%2C%20consisting%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%2C%20by%20capitalising%20on%20perceived%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20contested%2021%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2017%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20(SP)%2010.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20had%20the%20lowest%20strike%20rate%2C%20winning%20only%20nine%20of%20the%2021%20seats%20(43%25)%2C%20while%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%20had%20strike%20rates%20of%2076%25%20and%2080%25%2C%20winning%2013%20and%20eight%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disparity%20has%20led%20to%20concerns%20within%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20was%20allocated%20more%20seats%20than%20warranted%2C%20and%20that%20this%20should%20not%20serve%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20seat-sharing%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20wants%20to%20contest%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats%20again%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20Congress%20also%20aims%20to%20contest%20the%20most%20seats%2C%20arguing%20that%20both%20the%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20have%20weakened%20due%20to%20splits%20and%20no%20longer%20enjoy%20the%20same%20level%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20contested%20147%20seats%2C%20NCP%20(pre-split)%20121%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UPA%2C%20and%20the%20pre-split%20Shiv%20Sena%20126%20seats%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%20is%20another%20contentious%20issue.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20MVA%20leadership%20to%20decide%20whether%20he%20should%20be%20the%20alliance's%20CM%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20is%20advocating%20for%20a%20CM%20candidate%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20NCP%20(SP)%20prefer%20to%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20without%20a%20designated%20name%20and%20decide%20the%20top%20post%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20MLAs%20each%20party%20secures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20various%20seat-sharing%20formulas%20under%20consideration%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E1.%20A%20Third%20Each%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20formula%20proposes%20that%20all%20three%20parties%E2%80%94Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20NCP%20(SP)%2C%20and%20Congress%E2%80%94contest%20approximately%2090-95%20seats%20each%2C%20leaving%20the%20remainder%20for%20smaller%20parties.%20This%20approach%20is%20supported%20by%20their%20similar%20vote%20shares%20(16%25-17%25)%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E2.%20Based%20On%20MLAs%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20the%20Sena%20(pre-split)%20won%2056%20seats%2C%20the%20NCP%20(pre-split)%20won%2054%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%2044.%20These%20parties%20would%20have%20the%20first%20claim%20on%20these%20154%20seats.%20The%20remaining%20134%20seats%20would%20then%20be%20allocated%20based%20on%20current%20strength%2C%20historical%20performance%2C%20and%20recent%20general%20election%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20are%20no%20longer%20aligned%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Given%20that%20local%20candidates%20are%20crucial%20in%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20support%20for%20seats%20now%20held%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20factions%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E3.%20Based%20On%20Party%20Influence%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluence%20on%20a%20seat%20is%20determined%20by%20whether%20a%20party%20was%20a%20winner%20or%20runner-up.%20Since%202009%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20all%20parties%20except%20the%20BJP%20has%20declined%20in%20Maharashtra.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20influence%20over%20113%20seats%2C%20the%20Sena%20over%20110%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20over%20101%20-%20totalling%20324%20against%20an%20assembly%20strength%20of%20only%20288.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdjusting%20for%2039%20seats%20where%20the%20Congress%2FNCP%20was%20the%20winner%20and%20Sena%20was%20the%20runner-up%2C%20and%2032%20seats%20where%20Sena%20was%20the%20winner%20and%20Congress%2FNCP%20was%20the%20runner-up%2C%20the%20parties%20combined%20have%20influence%20over%20253%20seats%2C%20leaving%2035%20seats%20for%20further%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E4.%20Based%20On%20Party%20Strength%20Scanner%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strength%20scanner%20identifies%2050%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20Sena%20two%20or%20three%20times%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections%2C%2044%20seats%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%2043%20seats%20by%20the%20NCP.%20These%20137%20strong%20seats%20can%20be%20claimed%20by%20these%20parties.%20Additionally%2C%20167%20seats%20were%20won%20once%20by%20these%20parties%20in%20the%20last%20three%20polls%2C%20categorised%20as%20moderate.%20This%20results%20in%20a%20total%20of%20304%20seats%2C%2016%20more%20than%20the%20288%20assembly%20seats%2C%20allowing%20for%20adjustments%20due%20to%20double%20counting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20considerations%20are%20also%20crucial.%20The%20Congress%20is%20strong%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20parts%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Marathwada%3B%20the%20Sena%20is%20strong%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Thane-Konkan%20regions%3B%20the%20NCP%20is%20strong%20in%20Western%20Maharashtra%20and%20parts%20of%20North%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20leverage%20its%20strong%20Lok%20Sabha%20performance%20to%20secure%20a%20victory.%20Ticket%20distribution%20remains%20a%20challenge%20for%20NDA%20as%20well.%20A%20well-coordinated%20seat-sharing%20strategy%20could%20enhance%20MVA's%20prospects%2C%20with%20all%20parties%20needing%20to%20maintain%20unity%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20big%20picture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723439340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fn7mr4sng_sharad-pawar_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-maharashtra-polls-congress-sharad-pawar-negotiate-hard-with-uddhav-thackeray-6318361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20bloc%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20leverage%20its%20strong%20Lok%20Sabha%20performance%20to%20secure%20a%20victory.%20Ticket%20distribution%20remains%20a%20challenge%20for%20NDA%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-maharashtra-polls-congress-sharad-pawar-negotiate-hard-with-uddhav-thackeray-6318361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A