ing%2C%20boxing%20and%20judo%20is%20that%20of%20each%20athlete%20and%20his%20or%20her%20coach%20and%20NOT%20that%20of%20the%20IOA-appointed%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%20Dr.%20Dinshaw%20Pardiwala%20and%20his%20team%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Usha%C2%A0said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...the%20hate%20directed%20at%20the%20IOA%20medical%20team%2C%20especially%20Dr.%20Pardiwala%2C%20is%20unacceptable%20and%20worthy%20of%20condemnation.%26quot%3B%20She%20hoped%20that%20those%20rushing%20to%20judge%20the%20IOA%20medical%20team%20%26quot%3Bwould%20consider%20all%20facts%20before%20arriving%20at%20any%20conclusions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20had%20scripted%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20reach%20the%20gold%20medal%20bout%20in%20her%20category%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%20But%20her%20post-participation%20weight%20was%20found%20to%20have%20increased%20and%20despite%20all%20measures%2C%20which%20included%20cutting%20off%20Vinesh's%20hair%2C%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100gm%20extra%20during%20the%20morning%20weigh-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20Indian%20athlete%20in%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympic%20Games%20in%20such%20sport%20had%20his%20or%20her%20own%20support%20team.%20These%20support%20teams%20have%20been%20working%20with%20the%20athletes%20over%20so%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Usha%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IOA%20appointed%20a%20medical%20team%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20primarily%20as%20a%20team%20that%20would%20assist%20in%20the%20recovery%20and%20injury%20management%20of%20athletes%20during%20and%20after%20their%20competition.%20This%20team%20was%20also%20designed%20to%20support%20athletes%20who%20did%20not%20have%20their%20own%20team%20of%20nutritionists%20and%20physiotherapists.%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sports%20(CAS)%2C%20demanding%20that%20she%20be%20awarded%20a%20joint%20silver%20medal%20with%20Cuban%20wrestler%20Yusneylis%20Guzman%20Lopez%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20to%20the%20Indian%20but%20was%20later%20promoted%20to%20the%20final%20following%20the%20Haryana%20wrestler's%20disqualification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Sarah%20Hildebrandt%20won%20the%20gold%20after%20defeating%20Lopez%20in%20the%20title%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20on%20Vinesh's%20appeal%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20on%20August%2013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723436580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq3lks15_vinesh-phogat-afp_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fresponsibility-of-weight-management-pt-ushas-big-take-on-vinesh-phogat-row-6316455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drawing%20criticism%20for%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20weigh-in%20fiasco%2C%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20President%20PT%20Usha%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20athlete%20to%20manage%20their%20weight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A376%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fresponsibility-of-weight-management-pt-ushas-big-take-on-vinesh-phogat-row-6316455%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JD%20Vance's%20alleged%20drag%20queen%20photo%20leaks%3A%20LGBTQ%20hypocrisy%20accusations%20fly%2C%20campaign%20leaves%20questions%20unanswered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723436538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112456060%2Cimgsize-771759.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjd-vances-alleged-drag-queen-photo-leaks-lgbtq-hypocrisy-accusations-fly-campaign-leaves-questions-unanswered%2