uals%20from%20Jehanabad%20showed%20inconsolable%20families%20mourning%20their%20loss%20and%20the%20injured%20being%20treated%20at%20the%20local%20Makhdumpur%20and%20Sadar%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20present%20at%20the%20temple%20said%20there%20was%20a%20stampede%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20arrangements%20by%20the%20administration.%20Some%20NCC%20(National%20Cadet%20Corps)%20volunteers%20engaged%20in%20crowd%20management%20used%20'lathis'%20on%20the%20devotees%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20stampede%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20relative%20of%20a%20victim%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20fear%20the%20death%20count%20could%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20devotee%20present%20at%20the%20temple%20said%20the%20volunteers%20resorted%20to%20lathi-charge%20after%20a%20fight%20erupted%20involving%20a%20flower-seller.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20stampede%2C%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20there%20was%20no%20one%20from%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20happened%20due%20to%20the%20negligence%20of%20the%20police%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikash%20Kumar%2C%20sub-divisional%20officer%20(SDO)%2C%20Jehanabad%20denied%20that%20NCC%20volunteers%20used%20lathis%20to%20control%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20like%20that%20happened.%20This%20was%20an%20unfortunate%20incident.%20There%20was%20strict%20vigil.%20Adequate%20arrangements%20including%20force%20(NCC)%2C%20civil%20deputations%20and%20medical%20teams%20were%20made.%20We%20will%20give%20more%20details%20after%20the%20post-mortem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Magistrate%20Alankrita%20Pandey%20told%20PTI%20the%20stampede%20was%20a%20fallout%20of%20a%20dispute%20among%20kanwariyas%20that%20had%20led%20to%20a%20scuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723436460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F26r4v98o_bihar-stampede_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID