%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20both%20blue-collar%20and%20white-collar%20vacancies%20that%20are%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yana%20Lukashuk%2C%20head%20of%20recruitment%20at%20Lobby%20X%2C%20a%20Kyiv-based%20job%20agency.%20%26quot%3BMen%20who%20joined%20the%20Army%20and%20women%20with%20or%20without%20children%20who%20fled%20the%20country%20from%20all%20domains%20have%20formed%20a%20huge%20talent%20gap%20on%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuzmina%2C%20is%20one%20of%20two%20female%20employees%20at%20her%20power%20station%2C%20but%20is%20one%20of%20several%20women%20stepping%20up%20to%20fill%20blue-collar%20jobs%20that%20are%20now%20vacant%20because%20they%20were%20primarily%20occupied%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20and%20more%20female%20candidates%20are%20becoming%20factory%20workers%2C%20technicians%2C%20drivers%2C%20et%20cetera%20as%20they%20can%20do%20nothing%20else%20but%20to%20fill%20many%20important%20vacant%20jobs%20in%20some%20regions%20where%20men%20are%20lacking%2C%26quot%3B%20Lukashuk%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270ce80ed-b6bc-4f6e-bcf5-c22e4d9fe5b0%5C%22%3EEffects%20of%20a%20Soviet-era%20law%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20expert%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20trend%20is%20an%20especially%20notable%20feat%20because%20of%20a%20Soviet-era%20law%20that%20prohibited%20women%20from%20a%20list%20of%20about%20450%20occupations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20repealed%20the%20law%20in%202017%2C%20but%20its%20effects%20are%20still%20ingrained%20in%20society%2C%20said%20Olga%20Kupets%2C%20a%20labor%20economics%20professor%20at%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKyiv%20School%20of%20Economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20still%20some%20legal%20debate%20over%20whether%20the%20restrictions%20remain%2C%20and%20some%20coaches%20and%20lecturers%20in%20the%20vocational%20education%20system%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20train%20women%20yet%2C%20Kupets%20said.%20Even%20if%20those%20two%20issues%20can%20be%20overcome%2C%20there%20is%20strong%20pushback%20from%20society%2C%20according%20to%20Kupets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20people%2C%20lack%20of%20men%2C%20and%20there%20is%20official%20willingness%20from%20the%20government%20to%20help%20women%20work%20in%20these%20previously%20male%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20about%20government%20training%20programs%20that%20have%20been%20introduced%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20very%20low%20level%2C%20we%20see%20this%20huge%20opposition%20and%20resistance%20from%20employers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20cases%20of%20companies%20opening%20up%20roles%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20bosses%20discouraged%20women%20from%20applying%2C%20Kupets%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20discrimination%20in%20the%20labor%20market%20comes%20from%20stereotypes%2C%20not%20only%20from%20men%20but%20also%20from%20women%20like%20mothers%20or%20mothers-in-law%2C%26quot%3B%20Kupets%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Kuzmina%2C%20the%20electrician%2C%20said%20she%20sees%20women%20working%20around%20her%2C%20and%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20army%20but%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20could%20not%20be%20useful%20there%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuzmina%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20want%20to%20help%20our%20country%2C%20our%20Ukraine.%20I%20could%20not%20just%20sit%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20the%20war%20and%20how%20it%20has%20impacted%20your%20career%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20at%3A%20shubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-women-train-blue-collar-jobs-workforce-gap-war-electrician-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723430689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aa63e9aab37011780c0763%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-women-train-blue-collar-jobs-workforce-gap-war-electrician-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20war%20has%20created%20a%20big%20need%20for%20blue-collar%20workers%20in%20Ukraine.%20Women%2C%20like%2032-year-old%20Yuliia%20Kuzmina%2C%20are%20stepping%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-women-train-blue-collar-jobs-workforce-gap-war-electrician-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNothing%20More%20Unfair%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashwin's%20Critical%20Take%20On%20Return%20Of%20IPL%20Auction%20Rule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20criticised%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20rule%2C%20which%20could%20make%20its%20return%20during%20the%20auctions%20this%20year%20for%20the%20next%20year's%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%20The%20auction%20for%20the%20IPL%202025%20will%20be%20taking%20place%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%20Earlier%20in%20August%2C%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20organised%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstructive%20dialogue%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20ten%20league%20franchises%20on%20various%20subjects%20before%20formulating%20the%20IPL%20player%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20meeting%2C%20ESPNcricinfo%20reported%20that%20the%20significant%20points%20of%20discussion%3A%20Having%20mega%20auction%20every%20five%20years%20instead%20of%20three%2C%20the%20way%20it%20is%20right%20now%2C%20reinstating%20the%20right-to-match%20(RTM)%20card%20option%20at%20auctions%2C%20availability%2Fshortage%20of%20overseas%20players%20and%20a%20limit%20on%20total%20number%20of%20retentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERTM%20is%20a%20rule%20through%20which%20teams%20can%20automatically%20get%20the%20player%20which%20represented%20them%20in%20the%20previous%20season%20if%20they%20match%20the%20highest%20bid%20placed%20by%20a%20franchise.%20Teams%20used%20this%20rule%20in%20the%20past%20to%20get%20some%20valuable%20players%2C%20but%20in%20the%202021%20mega%20auction%2C%20it%20was%20removed%20in%20order%20to%20give%20the%20then-new%20franchises%2C%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20a%20wider%20pool%20of%20players%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20this%20rule%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Ashwin%20said%20that%20the%20rule%20is%20unfair%20to%20a%20player%20and%20does%20not%20give%20him%20a%20fair%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20rule%20more%20unfair%20for%20a%20player%20than%20RTM.%20Because%20how%20has%20the%20RTM%20rule%20been%20so%20far%3F%20For%20example%2C%20there%20is%20a%20player%20called%20X.%20He%20is%20on%20a%20team%20called%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20Sunrisers.%20His%20current%20value%20is%20around%20Rs%20five-six%20crores.%20He%20has%20gone%20into%20the%20auction.%20Now%20say%20Sunrisers%20want%20to%20buy%20the%20player%20back.%20So%2C%20the%20Sunrisers%20will%20bid%20for%20the%20player%20at%20a%20base%20price%20of%202%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20KKR%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20are%20bidding%20for%20the%20player.%20The%20bid%20goes%20up%20to%206%20crores%20and%20finally%2C%20they%20say%2C%20'The%20player%20is%20sold%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20for%206%20crores.'%20So%2C%20with%20RTM%2C%20the%20Sunrisers%20will%20then%20bid%20for%20and%20take%20the%20player%20at%206%20crores.%20The%20problem%20here%20is%20that%20Sunrisers%20are%20happy.%20But%20KKR%20and%20MI%20are%20unhappy.%20The%20only%20person%20(party)%20happy%20is%20Sunrisers.%20Because%2C%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20gave%20attendance%20bid%20at%20base%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ace-spinner%20said%20that%20RTM%20is%20unfair%20because%20it%20doesn't%20give%20fair%20value%20for%20the%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20there%20is%20no%20fair%20value%20at%20all.%20There%20is%20a%20bidder.%20The%20KKR%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%20are%20fighting.%20For%20one%20of%20those%20teams%2C%20it%20has%20gone%20up%20to%20six%20crores.%20What%20does%20SRH%20say%3F%20'You%20bought%20the%20player%2C%20right%3F%20Return%20the%20player%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20unfair.%20Because%2C%20at%20this%20time%2C%20SRH%20has%20to%20bid%20Rs%206.20%20crores%2C%20the%20other%20team%20Rs%206.40%20crores%20and%20they%20should%20reach%20the%20fair%20value%20of%20the%20player.%20The%20problem%20with%20RTM%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20fair%20value%20for%20the%20player.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20give%20three%20RTMs%20%5Bto%20each%20team%5D%2C%20the%20players%20will%20only%20go%20virtually%20empty-handed.%20Already%2C%20they%20do%20not%20get%20fair%20value%20in%20the%20auction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723430040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fiqk11iqg_ms-dhoni-and-ravichandran-ashwin-bcci_625x300_09_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnothing-more-unfair-r-ashwins-critical-take-on-return-of-ipl-auction-rule-6309763%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RTM%20is%20a%20rule%20through%20which%20teams%20can%20automatically%20get%20the%20player%20which%20represented%20them%20in%20the%20previous%20season%20if%20they%20match%20the%20highest%20bid%20placed%20by%20a%20franchise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rani%20Mukerji%2C%20Karan%20Johar%20to%20Address%20Australian%20Parliament%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723429800000%2C%22visual