p%3EBut%20with%20Koda%2C%20their%20total%20expenditure%20on%20that%20trip%20was%20around%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20longer%20trips%20with%20Koda%2C%20they%20set%20a%20maximum%20budget%20of%20%246%2C000%20for%20seven%20weeks.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20don't%20try%20to%20spend%20that%20much%2C%20but%20we%20definitely%20set%20a%20lot%20more%20aside%20for%20worst-case%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20Salley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20recalled%20a%20harrowing%20incident%20when%20Koda%20had%20diarrhea%2014%20times%20on%20the%20road.%20They%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20veterinarian%20and%20spent%20%241%2C100%20on%20X-rays%20and%20bloodwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20her%20golden%20retriever%20at%20the%20animal%20clinic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b08bad393cd3c8629b397b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20says%20they%20always%20set%20money%20aside%20in%20the%20event%20that%20Koda%20has%20to%20visit%20the%20vet.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Salley%20and%20Brianna%20Feehan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20we%20wasted%20two%20or%20three%20days%20just%20watching%20her%20go%20outside%20and%20be%20sick.%20It%20was%20awful%2C%26quot%3B%20Feehan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalley%20added%20that%20pet%20owners%20going%20on%20trips%20with%20their%20pets%20should%20consider%20buying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Fshould-i-get-pet-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epet%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20expect%20things%20to%20go%20as%20planned.%20there's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20curveball%20with%20an%20animal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288a30f3c-3f60-41a2-b9f6-fdc3f7396d78%5C%22%3EThey%20found%20Wyoming%20to%20be%20the%20dog-friendliest%20and%20Los%