dly%20accommodations%20%E2%80%94%20and%20were%20appalled%20when%20they%20saw%20that%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dogppl.co%2Fmembership%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edog%20park%20membership%20cost%20%24120%20monthly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20dogs%20live%20in%20LA%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20used%20to%20city%20life.%20So%2C%20we%20just%20pivot%20and%20go%20somewhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Feehan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3bf167e-a520-48c0-a973-11b7028895bb%5C%22%3ETheir%20next%20goal%20is%20to%20fly%20abroad%20with%20Koda%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20not%20alone.%20In%20June%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fadvisor%2Fpet-insurance%2Fbest-cities-to-travel-to-with-dog%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%20Advisor%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2010%2C000%20American%20dog%20owners%20found%20that%2033%25%20of%20respondents%20travel%20with%20their%20dogs%20by%20plane.%20Of%20the%20respondents%2C%2037%25%20also%20said%20that%20being%20unable%20to%20bring%20their%20dog%20on%20their%20travels%20is%20their%20top%20annoyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20pet%20owners%20prefer%20to%20travel%20with%20their%20pets%2C%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-your-pets-are-transported-on-commercial-airlines-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20simplifying%20the%20process%20to%20bring%20pets%20on%20board.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-fly-with-pets-policy-change-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20updated%20its%20policy%20in%20March%20to%20allow%20flyers%20to%20board%20with%20their%20pet%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20carry-on%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20number%20of%20shared%20private%20jet%20flights%20allows%20owners%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-with-pets-internation