se%20drone%20manufacturer%20DJI%20developed%20the%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20lifter%26quot%3B%20high-altitude%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMount%20Everest%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20landfill%20every%20year%20as%20crowds%20of%20adventurous%20climbers%20flock%20to%20its%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20have%20left%20an%20estimated%2050%20metric%20tons%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8yo7hskqSg0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20on%20Everest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20mountain%20is%20so%20full%20of%20garbage%20that%20people%20have%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20highest%20garbage%20dump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENepal%20has%20tried%20all%20kinds%20of%20solutions%2C%20including%20a%20mandate%20that%20climbers%20collect%20and%20carry%20out%2018%20pounds%20of%20garbage%20every%20time%20they%20visit%20or%20pay%20a%20fee%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20mostly%2C%20however%2C%20fallen%20on%20the%20literal%20shoulders%20of%20the%20Sherpa%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8yo7hskqSg0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20live%20in%20the%20high%20mountainous%20regions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20Sherpa%20guides%20who%20help%20climbers%20navigate%20the%20mountains%20also%20gather%20trash%20and%20supplies%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20garbage%20is%20so%20overwhelming%20that%20carrying%20it%20out%20has%20proven%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECue%20the%20giant%20flying%20garbage%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENepal%20plans%20to%20deploy%20unmanned%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20lifter%26quot%3B%20drones%20that%20sound%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bswarm%20of%20bees%26quot%3B%20to%20remove%20the%20trash%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2024%2F08%2F05%2Fit-s-official-chinese-drones-will-fly-trash-out-of-everest-slopes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20high-altitude%20drones%20could%20also%20help%20lay%20rope%20lines%20and%20prepare%20routes%20for%20climbers%2C%20reducing%20their%20reliance%20on%20Sherpas%20and%20possibly%20reducing%20injuries%20and%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20were%20developed%20and%20manufactured%20by%20Chinese%20drone%20maker%20Da%20Jiang%20Innovations.%20DJI%20also%20makes%20consumer%20drones%20popular%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20has%20been%20the%20target%20of%20a%20proposed%20ban%20for%20national%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20delivered%20its%20first%20drone%20to%20Everest%20in%20April%20for%20a%20test%20run.%20A%20single%20drone%20was%20able%20to%20carry%20500%20pounds%20of%20garbage%20an%20hour%20between%20two%20camps%20at%20Everest's%20base%2C%20a%20feat%20that%20would%20normally%20require%20over%20a%20dozen%20Sherpas%20and%20take%20six%20hours%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Kathmandu%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJagat%20Bhusal%2C%20chief%20administration%20officer%20of%20the%20rural%20municipality%20that%20is%20home%20to%20Everest%2C%20told%20the%20Post%20that%20using%20the%20drones%20will%20help%20the%20Sherpas%20avoid%20navigating%20the%20%26quot%3Bdangers%20in%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20is%20a%201.6-mile%20stretch%20of%20slowly%20cascading%20ice%20just%20above%20Base%20Camp%20on%20Everest's%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Col%26quot%3B%20route.%20The%202024%20Everest%20climbing%20season%20was%20delayed%20by%2012%20days%20in%20May%20after%20rising%20temperatures%20caused%20the%20glacier%20ice%20to%20crumble.%20Just%20last%20year%2C%20an%20avalanche%20on%20the%20Khumbu%20killed%20three%20Sherpas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20up%20there%20one%20part%20of%20the%20day%20and%20coming%20down%20the%20next%20day%20could%20look%20very%20different%2C%20and%20the%20probability%20of%20that%20getting%20worse%20with%20a%20warmer%20climate%20increases%2C%26quot%3B