0monsoon.%20Imagine%20gallons%20of%20rainwater%20flowing%20down%20the%20drain%20and%20flooding%20the%20city.%20Lakes%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20capture%20that%20rainwater%2C%20which%20can%20then%20support%20the%20city%20during%20the%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20miles%20away%20from%20India%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20in%20the%20US%20since%202015%2C%20but%20this%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20affected%20the%20organisation%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20only%20grown%20since%20then.%20Although%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20visit%20home%20often%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20my%20parents%20angry!%20%E2%80%94%20I%20ensure%20to%20return%20to%20India%20once%20every%20year%20to%20monitor%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20cannot%20do%20this%20work%20alone.%20Bengaluru%20alone%20has%20200%20lakes.%20If%20we%20rejuvenate%2010%20each%20year%2C%20it%20will%20take%20us%2020%20more%20years.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20have%20that%20much%20time.%20People%20can%20join%20hands%20with%20us%20so%20that%20together%20we%20can%20rejuvenate%20more%20and%20more%20lakes%20and%20be%20responsible%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVolunteer%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saytrees.org%2Fvolunteer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESayTrees%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20build%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20SayTrees)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%2