20replaced%20over%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azhar%20is%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360465%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAzhar%20manufactures%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20on%20the%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20drew%20his%20inspiration%20from%20a%20biopolymer%20research%20paper%20dating%20back%20to%20the%201800s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20studying%20about%20a%20biodegradable%20polymer%2C%20PBAT%20(Polybutylene%20adipate-co-terephthalate)%2C%20that%20is%20derived%20from%20plant-based%20sources%20such%20as%20corn%20and%20potatoes.%20This%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20new%20business%20endeavour%20for%20Azhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20was%20to%20find%20the%2