Azhar%20had%20to%20shut%20the%20factory%20down%20after%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20make%20profits%20to%20sustain%20the%20company.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20back%20to%20zero.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20had%2014-15%20backlogs%20in%20my%20engineering.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20balance%20both%20jobs%2C%20I%20failed%20at%20both.%20It%20was%20a%20stressful%20situation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20through%20sheer%20grit%20and%20relentless%20effort%2C%20the%20civil%20engineer%20not%20only%20cleared%20all%20exams%20but%20also%20secured%20a%20funding%20from%20an%20investor%2C%20and%20eventually%20revived%20his%20enterprise%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20company%20is%20manufacturing%204-5%20lakh%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345783%2Fyellowbag-in-madurai-traditional-tamil-cloth-bags-plastic-waste-krishnan-subramanian-gowri-gopinath-earn-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20Interestingly%2C%20Azhar%20says%2C%20these%20bags%20are%20compostable%20and%20can%20be%20decomposed%20within%20180%20days.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20his%20startup%20has%20replaced%20more%20than%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags%20by%20commercialising%20in%20the%20B2B%20chain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20clocked%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.8%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohd%20Sami%20Uddin%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Country%20Chicken%20Co%2C%20has%20been%20using%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20Sharing%20his%20feedback%2C%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20Prior%20to%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%2C%20we%20were%20using%20plastic%20bags.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20also%20tried%20ot