es.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20larger%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20this%20one%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20genset%20generators%20for%20backup%20power.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20these%20generators%20produce%20a%20humming%20noise%20that%20can%20disturb%20the%20local%20birdlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20forest%2C%20our%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20the%20birds%2C%20leopards%2C%20mountain%20goats%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20other%20wildlife%20that%20call%20this%20place%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains.%20To%20protect%20the%20surrounding%20animals%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20lighting%20dim%20and%20the%20music%20at%20a%20low%20volume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20offerings%2C%20the%20couple%20leads%20tourists%20to%20unexplored%20spots%20such%20as%20the%20Kalagarh%20forest.%20They%20offer%20stays%20in%20forest%20bungalows%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20lanterns%20and%20camping%20chairs%20as%20many%20lack%20electricity.%20They%20also%20arrange%20for%20guests%20to%20dine%20at%20local%20homes%2C%20thanks%20to%20their%20connection%20with%20residents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20something%20they%20really%20enjoy%20and%20adds%20an%20authentic%20touch%20to%20their%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20notes.%20They%20also%20introduce%20guests%20to%20forest%20guards%20who%20live%20in%20isolation%20and%20rarely%20interact%20with%20outsiders.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20guards%20are%20always%20delighted%20to%20meet%20new%20people%20and%20have%20many%20stories%20to%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20created%20by%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20was%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20Kalagarh%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharashtra-heritage-stay-hotel-sustainable-tents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserving%20as%20both%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20a%20tourism%20spot.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Their%20success%20drew%20visitors%20from%20all%20over%20India%20and%20internationally%2C%20prompting%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20resorts%20and%20properties%20in%20the%20forested%20region.%20This%20expansion%20has%20created%20job%20opportunities%20for%20locals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20people%20here%20are%20now%20employed%20in%20the%20service%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20running%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20the%20duo%20now%20works%20as%20naturalists%2C%20leading%20excursions%20to%20hidden%20gems%20like%20the%20Kalagarh%20Tiger%20Reserve%20National%20Park%20and%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20where%20they%20are%20presently%20designing%20a%20wildlife%20lodge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20training%20from%20Taj%20Hotels%2C%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20conduct%20trips%20to%20forest%20bungalows%20while%20adhering%20to%20forest%20regulations%2C%20such%20as%20specific%20arrival%20and%20safari%20times.%20Government%20permits%20are%20acquired%20before%20each%20trip%2C%20and%20careful%20planning%20is%20done%20well%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-17_11zon-1723128254.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Besides%20running%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20the%20duo%20now%20works%20as%20naturalists%2C%20leading%20excursions%20to%20hidden%20gems.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-17_11zon-1723128254.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-17_11zon-1723128254-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-17_11zon-1723128254-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-