ims%20%3C%2Fa%3Estage%20itself.%20He%20says%20that%20he%20joined%20a%20coaching%20institute%20and%20only%20relied%20on%20coaching%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20read%20the%20standard%20books%20like%20Polity%20by%20M%20Laxmikanth%20and%20Modern%20History%20Spectrum.%20Learn%20to%20optimise%20your%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20understand%20what%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20study.%20Conduct%20a%20trend%20analysis%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20questions%20that%20are%20asked%20in%20both%20prelims%20and%20Mains.%20Prepare%20accordingly.%20Do%20not%20waste%20your%20time%20mugging%20up%20from%20various%20sources.%20Once%20you%20learn%20filtering%20out%20important%20information%2C%20then%20the%20syllabus%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20vast%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Do%20not%20neglect%20current%20affairs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%20aspirants%20are%20advised%20to%20read%20The%20Hindu%20or%20The%20Indian%20Express%20newspapers%20%E2%80%93%20both%20available%20only%20in%20English.%20Vikas%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20comprehend%20the%20language%2C%20then%20regularly%20follow%20YouTube%20channels%20that%20organise%20editorial%20discussions.%20For%20instance%2C%20check%20out%20Harshit%20Dwivedi%20and%20Prashant%20Tiwari%20who%20provide%20current%20affair%20notes%20on%20Telegram%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th