3E%2C%20dug%20around%20and%20found%20Abraham%E2%80%99s%20real%20name%2C%20location%20and%20phone%20number.%20He%20promptly%20passed%20this%20information%20to%20other%20forum%20members%20who%20were%20mostly%20American%2C%20hoping%20that%20they%20would%20act%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENobody%20did%20anything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20time%20before%20social%20media%2C%20smartphones%20and%20unlimited%20calling%2C%20Dushyant%20woke%20his%20parents%20up%20in%20a%20panic%2C%20activated%20international%20calling%20on%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20phone%20and%20called%20the%20Miami%20police%20department%E2%80%99s%20emergency%20line.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20fighting%20tears%2C%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20to%20convey%20to%20them%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%20and%20they%20kept%20transferring%20me%20to%20different%20people%2C%20until%20they%20connected%20me%20to%20someone%20who%20told%20me%20that%20his%20phone%20was%20from%20the%20Broward%20County%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20that%20I%20should%20contact%20the%20Sheriff%20of%20that%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dushyant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dushyant%2C%20Batman%20of%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-150x79.jpg%2