%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20firmly%20on%20Sreejesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterfinal%20against%20Great%20Britain%20marked%20the%2023rd%20time%20Sreejesh%20stood%20in%20goal%20for%20India%20during%20a%20shoot-out%2C%20securing%20victory%20on%2013%20occasions.%20His%20performance%20was%20so%20extraordinary%20that%20a%20British%20coach%20watching%20from%20the%20stands%20exclaimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuperman!%E2%80%9D%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20abilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreejesh%20comes%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20in%20Kizhakkambalam%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Kochi%2C%20Kerala.%20Born%20into%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20he%20was%20fueled%20by%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifice.%20Recognising%20his%20talent%2C%20his%20father%20had%20sold%20their%20cow%20to%20purchase%20a%20hockey%20kit%20for%20young%20Sreejesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20struggle%20had%20just%20begun%20for%20him.%20Sreejesh%20was%20constantly%20mocked%20for%20his%20looks%2C%20traditional%20attire%20(%3Cem%3Eveshti)%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Malayalam%20accent.%20Being%20told%20that%20a%20Kerala%20player%20would%20never%20make%20it%20big%20in%20Indian%20hockey%2C%20there%20were%20times%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20But%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifices%20kept%20him%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreejesh%20practised%20day%20and%20night%2C%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20junior%20hockey%20team.%20He%20won%20three%20Asian%20Games%20medals%2C%20including%20gold%20in%20Hangzhou%202022%2C%20which%20secured%20India%E2%80%99s%20spot%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359575%2Folympics-avinash-sable-india-paris-steeplechase-gold-medal-at-asian-games-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Named%20FIH%E2%80%99s%20(International%20Hockey%20Federation)%20best%20goalkeeper%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20he%20silenced%20his%20critics%20with%20his%20stellar%20performance.