things%20we%20disliked%20as%20children.%20This%20third%20generation%20farmer%2C%20too%2C%20would%20find%20a%20deep%20set%20passion%20in%20farming%2C%20and%20ultimately%20make%20a%20career%20out%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20middlemen%20from%20ripping%20off%20their%20earnings%2C%20Aprajita%20started%20selling%20their%20farm%20fresh%20apples%20directly%20online%20in%202021.%20In%20just%20two%20hours%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20300%20kg%2C%20ensuring%20that%20her%20parents%20received%20the%20right%20value%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20robust%20Instagram%20community%20helped%20as%20they%20immediately%20jumped%20on%20to%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20fresh%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20registered%20her%20brand%20name%20%E2%80%98Phal%20Phool%E2%80%99%20through%20which%20she%20sells%20apples%2C%20flower%2C%20pulses%20%26amp%3B%20vegetable%20seeds%20directly%20to%20customers.%20The%20engineer%20quit%20her%20job%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20to%20pursue%20farming%20full%20time%2C%20with%20dreams%20of%20practising%20permaculture%20and%20creating%20a%20food%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20desire%20to%20help%20her%20father%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAprajita%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20a%20job%20in%202017.%20When%20she%20visited%20the%20market%2C%20she%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20the%20prices%20of%20apples!%20While%20her%20parents%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20for%20their%20produce%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20middlemen%20giving%20them%20a%20pittance%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20apples%20were%20being%20sold%20for%20almost%20Rs%20300%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9PpVFqyiVi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%