w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359752%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20Bachittar%20a%20year%20to%20make%20the%20first%20sale%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20PAU.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debt-ridden%20farmer%20was%20forced%20to%20sell%2015-acre%20of%20his%20farmland%20%E2%80%94%20his%20only%20treasure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20take%20the%20decision%20of%20selling%20my%20farmland.%20For%20any%20farmer%2C%20his%20land%20is%20his%20only%20treasure.%20I%20was%20so%20depressed%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20out%20of%20my%20home%20for%20a%20year%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20weddings%20or%20local%20events%20for%20four%20years.%20I%20would%20make%20excuses%20to%20avoid%20speaking%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20some%20time%20had%20passed%2C%20he%20recollected%20a%20trade%20fair%20which%20he%20attended%20in%20Delhi%20in%201993%2C%20showcasing%20the%20advantages%20of%20soybean%20cultivation%20and%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20newfound%20determination%2C%20he%20underwent%20training%20in%20preparing%20soy%20milk%20and%20soy%20paneer%20from%20the%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Agricultural%20Engineering%20(CIAE)%2C%20Bhopal%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%2C%20he%20established%20a%20small%20one-room%20factory%20to%20produce%20soy%20milk%20and%20tofu.%20Without%20any%20other%20modes%20of%20marketing%20the%20products%2C%20he%20started%20giving%20them%20as%20samples%20to%20customers%20that%20came%20to%20his%20grocery%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20challenging%20to%20market%20this%20product%20in%20a%20place%20where%20people%20preferred%20cow%20and%20buffalo%20milk.%20So%2C%20even%20though%20they%20liked%20its%20taste%2C%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20purchase%20it.%20My%20family%20also%20questioned%20me%20why%20I%20was%20manufacturing%20it%20when%20I%20had%20no%20customers.%20But%20I%20believed%20in%20myself%20that%20one%20day%2C%20this%20work%20would%20scale%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20make%20the%20first%20sale%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20PAU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bachittar%20is%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20the%20local%20officials%20who%20helped%20him%20market%20the%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-2-1722848919-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359750%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBachittar%20is%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20the%20local%20officials%20who%20helped%20him%20market%20the%20products.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Mandeep%20Singh%2C%20Associate%20Director%20of%20Training%20at%20the%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%20under%20PAU%20in%20Sangrur%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20giving%20a%20platform%20to%20Bachittar%20to%20set%20up%20stalls%20at%20the%20KVK%20and%20boost%20his%20work.%20We%20also%20promote%20his%20products%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekisan%20mela%20%3C%2Fem%3E(farmer%E2%80%99s%20fair).%20It%20is%20immensely%20satisfying%20to%20see%20him%20succeed%20after%20years%20of%20struggle.%20We%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20promote%20value-addition%20and%20processing%20of%20products%20for%20extra%20incomes%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bachittar%20has%20established%20an%20automatic%20soybean%20processing%20plant.%20Depending%20on%20the%20demand%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20freshly%20prepares%20up%20to%20700%20litres%20of%20milk%20and%20four%20quintals%20of%20tofu%20daily.%20This%20earns%20him%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2010-12%20lakh%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBachittar%20has%20trained%20his%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Karanveer%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20the%20processing%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaranveer%2C%20who%20has%20been%20helping%20him%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20not%20only%20taught%20me%20the%20processing%20work%20but%20also%20the%20learnings%20of%20his%20life.%20We%20should%20not%20give%20up%20on%20hard%20work%20irrespective%20of%20ups%20and%20downs.%20Although%20he%20has%20trained%20me%2C%20he%20still%20goes%20to%20work%20every%20day%20despite%20his%20age.%20It%E2%80%99s%20truly%20inspirational.%20Seeing%20him%2C%20I%20wonder%20why%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20as%20active%20as%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20he%20has%20received%20numerous%20awards%20including%20the%20State%20Award%20in%202003%20and%20the%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20National%20Award%20in%202004.%20He%20was%20also%20facilitated%20with%20soil%20beverage%20of%20the%20year%202023%20award%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20Indian%20soy%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bachittar%20says%2C%20he%20reinvested%20his%20earnings%20into%20purchasing%20the%20land%20he%20had%20previously%20sold%2C%20reclaiming%20the%20ownership%20of%20seven%20out%20of%20the%2015%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20to%20get%2