ved%20reality%20for%20millions%20like%20Sumit%20Kumar%2C%20a%20construction%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Gopalganj%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Sumit%20had%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work.%20He%20walked%20for%20two%20days%20before%20hitching%20rides%20on%20buses%20and%20trucks%20to%20reach%20home%2C%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20one%20week%20it%20took%20to%20reach%20home%20was%20the%20worst%20week%20of%20my%20life.%20There%20was%20nobody%20willing%20to%20help%20me%20in%20the%20area%20where%20I%20lived.%20I%20survived%20thanks%20to%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20other%20workers%20like%20me.%20I%20vowed%20never%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20who%20wished%20to%20work%20near%20his%20hometown.%20The%20nightmarish%20experience%20during%20the%20lockdown%20made%20many%20workers%20desire%20the%20same%2C%20but%20where%20were%20the%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20country%20started%20opening%20up%20slowly%2C%20people%20had%20to%20maintain%20a%20six-foot%20distance%20in%20public%20places.%20How%20could%20100%20workers%20in%20a%20small%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20maintain%20distance%3F%20To%20understand%20their%20problems%20in%20detail%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20spent%20over%20four%20months%20assessing%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20Bihar%2C%20Noida%2C%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sector%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20agriculture.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Knight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%20as%20of%202023%2C%20out%20of%20which%20over%2080%20percent%20are%20unskilled.%20When%20Chandrashekhar%20came%20across%20this%20statistic%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20major%20gap%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-bl